# Projection: GMEOW → pure vcard. GENERATED by `gmeow regenerate` (mappings) from mapping-dsl/ — DO NOT EDIT.
# Lossy and directional by design; drops: the postal reference frame (axes, topological kind, metric) is dropped; only the flat vcard:Address component values and composed label survive; the birth Participation (role, period, confidence, standpoint) and fuzzy-date bounds are dropped; only the principal's birth instant survives as vcard:bday; non-displayable names (deadnames) dropped; elevation is dropped; the coordinate reference frame (WGS84) is implicit in the geo: URI; contact-point usage context and validity drop; the bare email edge survives; contact-point usage context and validity drop; the bare IM edge survives; contact-point usage context and validity drop; the bare telephone edge survives; the five declined forms are preserved in full (lossless for the declension); only the non-specifying values (any/ask/name-only, which carry no forms) and any period or standpoint are not represented; the Membership relator (organization, period, role, confidence, standpoint) collapses to a flat vcard:title literal; contested membership claims are not distinguished.
PREFIX gmeow: <https://blackcatinformatics.ca/gmeow/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX vcard: <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#>
PREFIX vcardx: <https://blackcatinformatics.ca/vcard-ext/>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>

CONSTRUCT {
